"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?21/24/21894?source=see_link\">",
"     Patient information: Depression treatment options for adults (Beyond the Basics)",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
