"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/10/3241?source=see_link\">",
"     Treatment of premenstrual syndrome and premenstrual dysphoric disorder",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <br/>",
