"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"centered\">",
"        N",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td colspan=\"4\">",
"        Do condoms, diaphragms or latex sexual aids cause itching or swelling?",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"centered\">",
"        Y",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"centered\">",
"        N",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td colspan=\"4\">",
"        Do rubber handles, rubber bands or elastic bands or clothing cause any discomfort?",
"       </td>",
